'''《宋飞的视野》'''（{{lang|en|SeinfeldVision}}）是[[美国|美国]][[情景喜剧|情景喜剧]]《[[我为喜剧狂|我为喜剧狂]]》[[我为喜剧狂_(第2季)|第2季]]的第1集，也是整个剧集的第22集，由该剧主创人、[[执行制片人|执行制片人]]兼女主演[[蒂娜·菲|蒂娜·菲]]编剧， 唐·斯卡迪诺执导<ref name="crew" />，2007年10月4日通过[[全国广播公司|全国广播公司]]在美国[[首演|首播]]<ref name="pressrelease_mediavillage">{{cite web |url=http://www.screenrush.co.uk/television/television-813/season-5594/ |title=30 Rock: Episodes Season 2 |publisher=Screenrush (AlloCiné) |accessdate=2013-08-22 |location=London |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120730001603/http://www.screenrush.co.uk/television/television-813/season-5594/ |archivedate=2012-07-30 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

这一集的故事发生在2007年秋，全国广播公司[[喜剧小品|喜剧小品]]《{{lang|en|TGS}}与崔西·乔丹》准备给最新一季做开场。首席编剧丽兹·莱蒙（{{lang|en|Liz Lemon}}，蒂娜·菲饰）与男友弗洛伊德·德巴伯（{{lang|en|Floyd DeBarber}}，[[杰森·苏戴奇斯|杰森·苏戴奇斯]]饰）分手后也希望给出一个合适的了结，副总裁杰克·唐纳吉（{{lang|en|Jack Donaghy}}，[[亚历克·鲍德温|亚历克·鲍德温]]饰）计划推出一个名叫《宋飞的视野》的节目，为期一个月。女演员简娜·玛隆妮（{{lang|en|Jenna Maroney}}，{{link-en|简·科拉克斯基|Jane Krakowski}}饰）在暑期患上了[[肥胖症|肥胖症]]，因此急需[[减肥|减肥]]。[[电视台|电视台]]杂工跟班肯尼期·帕塞尔（{{lang|en|Kenneth Parcell}}，[[杰克·麦克布瑞尔|杰克·麦克布瑞尔]]）成了男演员崔西·乔丹（{{lang|en|Tracy Jordan}}，[[崔西·摩根|崔西·摩根]]）的“办公室老婆”，丽兹的小助理施乐·泽洛克斯（{{lang|en|Cerie Xerox}}，[[卡特里娜·宝登|卡特里娜·宝登]]饰）在给自己的婚礼作准备<ref name="pressrelease_mediavillage" /><ref name="seinfeldvision">{{cite episode |title=SeinfeldVision |series=30 Rock |serieslink=我为喜剧狂 |credits=Writer(s): Tina Fey; Director: Don Scardino |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2007-10-04 |season=2 |number=1}}</ref>。这集节目获得了电视评论员较好的评价。

==剧情==
首席编剧丽兹·莱蒙回到《TGS与崔西·乔丹》剧组后<ref name="pilot">{{cite episode |title=Pilot |episodelink=试播集 (我为喜剧狂) |series=30 Rock |credits=Writer: Tina Fey; Director: Don Scardino |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2006-10-11 |season=1 |number=1}}</ref>来到副总裁杰克的[[办公室|办公室]]，对方表示自己打算推出一个名为《宋飞的视野》的[[电视节目|电视节目]]，这个节目将由杰瑞·宋飞主持，为期一个月，介时有望把情景喜剧《[[宋飞传|宋飞传]]》的片断用到节目中。杰瑞·宋飞得知这一方案后来到电视台找杰克对质，双方经过商议决定把节目的时间缩短到只播出一个晚上。

丽兹在夏季时和远在[[克利夫兰_(俄亥俄州)|克利夫兰]]的男友弗洛伊德[[分手|分手]]了，她打算给这段恋情一个了结<ref name="hiatus">{{cite episode |title=Hiatus |episodelink=裂缝 (我为喜剧狂) |series=30 Rock |credits=Writer: Tina Fey; Director: Don Scardino |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2007-04-26 |season=1 |number=21}}</ref>，遇到宋飞时两人短暂交谈，对方给了她正需要的建议，于是她鼓起勇气给弗洛伊德打[[电话|电话]]，只是没想到接电话的却是另外一个女人。助理施乐邀请丽兹和节目女演员简娜·玛隆妮作自己的[[伴娘|伴娘]]，两人都接受了，施乐于是带她们去选购[[结婚|结婚]]礼服，中间丽兹被问起要不要亲自试穿一件时，她决定直接买一件。

简娜自出演了[[音乐剧|音乐剧]]版本的《[[现代灰姑娘|现代灰姑娘]]》后就变得很胖，她想方设法避免被他人发现这一点但还是无济于事。节目的头号明星崔西·乔丹和太太安吉·乔丹（{{lang|en|Angie Jordan}}）分居了，于是他选择住在自己的[[化妆|化妆]]室，电视台的杂工跟班肯尼斯“担任”他的“办公室老婆”，这份“新工作”需要肯尼斯给予崔西“无微不至的关怀”。

==制作==
2007年7月，蒂娜·菲和执行制片人{{link-en|洛恩·迈克尔斯|Lorne Michaels}}在一次[[电视评论家协会|电视评论家协会]]的年度活动上宣布[[杰瑞·宋飞|杰瑞·宋飞]]将参加《我为喜剧狂》第2季开场节目的[[演出|演出]]<ref name="tca_1">{{cite news |first=Stuart |last=Levine |title=TCA: Jerry Seinfeld Back at ''30 Rock'' |url=http://weblogs.variety.com/on_the_air/2007/07/tca-seinfeld-ba.html |publisher=''Variety'' |date=2007-07-16 |accessdate=2013-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120207055725/http://weblogs.variety.com/on_the_air/2007/07/tca-seinfeld-ba.html |archivedate=2012-02-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。自1998年的情景喜剧《[[宋飞传|宋飞传]]》完结后，宋飞只在两部电视剧中出现过，分别是《{{link-en|我为卿狂 (电视剧)|Mad About You|我为卿狂}}》和《{{link-en|纽约电台新闻时段|Newsradio}}》<ref name="seinfeldinterview_1">{{cite web |url=http://www.ugo.com/tv/30-rock/?cur=seinfeld |title=Jerry Seinfeld Interview |accessdate=2008-03-29 |last=Braun |first=Kyle |publisher=''UGO'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071025023009/http://www.ugo.com/tv/30-rock/?cur=seinfeld |archivedate=2007-10-25 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="seinfeldmay">{{cite news |title=''Mad About You'': Season Opener – Cast & Crew |url=http://movies.msn.com/movies/movie-cast-and-crew/mad-about-you-season-opener/ |publisher=''MSN'' |accessdate=2013-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120902040743/http://movies.msn.com/movies/movie-cast-and-crew/mad-about-you-season-opener/ |archivedate=2012-09-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="seasonopener_mad">{{cite episode |title=Season Opener |series=Mad About You |credits=Writer(s): Victor Levin; Director: Michael Lembeck |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=1998-09-22 |season=7 |number=1}}</ref>。

剧中杰瑞·宋飞的出场镜头于2007年8月20日摄制<ref name="filmingphotos">{{cite web |url=http://www.flickr.com/photos/mokenilworth/4298431053/ |title=''30 Rock'': 'SeinfeldVision'' Episode 201 – Pictured: (l-r) Jerry Seinfeld as Himself, Jack McBrayer as Kenneth |accessdate=2008-03-29 |last=Haston |first=Chris |date=2007-09-26 |work=Set Photos |publisher=''NBC Universal Media Village'' |archive-date=2013-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130822022517/http://www.flickr.com/photos/mokenilworth/4298431053 |dead-url=no }} Save Picture as → Right click file → Properties → Summary → Advanced → Date Picture Taken</ref>，他在出场时戴有一顶假发，来让自己和《宋飞传》中的形象更为接近。起初戴上假发时宋飞觉得“这看上去真古怪”，[[妻子|妻子]]告诉他，《宋飞传》中的他看上去就是这么副模样<ref name="tinainterview_1">{{cite web |url=http://www.buddytv.com/articles/30-rock/tina-fey-talks-about-jerry-sei-11216.aspx |title=Tina Fey Talks About Jerry Seinfeld's Guest Stint on ''30 Rock'' |accessdate=2013-08-22 |last=Claustro |first=Lisa |date=2007-09-20 |publisher=''BuddyTV'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081029071113/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/30-rock/tina-fey-talks-about-jerry-sei-11216.aspx |archivedate=2008-10-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。这一集中给丽兹与弗洛伊德自[[我为喜剧狂_(第1季)|第1季]]的《[[熬夜_(我为喜剧狂)|熬夜]]》开始的恋情<ref name="upallnight">{{cite episode |title=Up All Night |series=30 Rock |credits=Writer: Tina Fey; Director: Michael Engler |network=NBC Universal |station=NBC |airdate=2007-02-08 |season=1 |number=13}}</ref>做出了结，剧中原本还有一个把施乐·泽洛克斯的姓氏“{{lang|en|Xerox}}”与同名品牌[[施乐|施乐]]（英文名称也是“{{lang|en|Xerox}}”）联系起来的笑话，但这个情节最后剪去了没有播出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eonline.com/news/4154/exclusive-30-rock-scores-will-arnett-chris-kattan-and-mariah-carey-in-our-dreams |title=Exclusive! ''30 Rock'' Scores Will Arnett, Chris Kattan and Mariah Carey (in Our Dreams) |accessdate=2013-08-22 |last=Dos Santos |first=Kristin |coauthors=Godwin, Jennifer |date=2008-03-08 |publisher=''E!'' |archive-date=2013-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130822031331/http://www.eonline.com/news/4154/exclusive-30-rock-scores-will-arnett-chris-kattan-and-mariah-carey-in-our-dreams |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《宋飞的视野》是卡特里娜·宝登、凯斯·鲍威尔（{{lang|en|Keith Powell}}）和朗尼·罗斯（{{lang|en|Lonny Ross}}）首度以主要演员的身份参加演出，他们的名字也首次出现在片头的演员名单上<ref name="carlockinterview">{{cite web |url=http://www.eonline.com/gossip/kristin/detail/index.jsp?uuid=8af9b8c0-fbde-4b8b-8353-237b3c459a8e |title=Exclusive! ''30 Rock'' Scores Will Arnett, Chris Kattan and Mariah Carey (in Our Dreams) |accessdate=2008-06-23 |last=Dos Santos |first=Kristen |date=2008-03-04 |publisher=''E! Online'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080623024746/http://www.eonline.com/gossip/kristin/detail/index.jsp?uuid=8af9b8c0-fbde-4b8b-8353-237b3c459a8e |archivedate=2008-06-23 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="imdbcredits">{{cite web |title=''30 Rock'' - Full cast and crew |accessdate=2013-08-13 |publisher=Internet Movie Database |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0496424/fullcredits |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111230000539/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0496424/fullcredits |archivedate=2011-12-30 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

==反响==
《宋飞的视野》在美国首播时吸引了约733万户[[家庭|家庭]]收看<ref name="ratings_1">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2007/scene/news/friday-night-lights-lights-up-nbc-1117973599/ |title=''Friday Night Lights'' Lights up NBC |accessdate=2013-08-22 |last=Kissell |first=Rick |date=2007-10-07 |publisher=''Variety'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081012111637/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117973599.html?categoryid=1275&cs=1 |archivedate=2008-10-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="weeklyrankings">{{cite web |title=Ratings |publisher=The Futon Critic |work=TheFutonCritic.com |date=2007-10-09 |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/ratings/2007/10/09/nbc-ties-for-number-1-in-18-49-for-a-second-week-in-a-row-and-remains-tied-for-the-season-to-date-lead-25668/20071009nbc02/ |accessdate=2013-08-22}}</ref>，在这个星期所有的电视节目中名列第6位<ref name="weeklyrankings" />。这也是当时除有813万户家庭观看的《[[试播集_(我为喜剧狂)|试播集]]》外《我为喜剧狂》收视率最高的一集<ref name="pilotratings_variety">{{cite news |first=Rick |last=Kissell |title=NBC's ''Rock'' solid in premiere |url=http://variety.com/2006/scene/news/nbc-s-rock-solid-in-premiere-1117951807/ |publisher=''Variety'' |date=2006-10-12 |accessdate=2013-07-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106184459/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117951807?refCatId=1275 |archivedate=2012-11-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，在18-49岁年龄段人群中收获了3.4 / 9的收视率，这意味着全美18-49岁年龄段人群里有3.4%看了这集，而播出时有看电视的该年龄段观众群里则有9%选择收看《宋飞的视野》<ref name="ratings_1" />。

[[Image:Jerry_Seinfeld_(1997).jpg|180px]]》的亚历山大·斯坦利批评杰瑞·宋飞在本集节目中为自己配音的动画长片《[[蜜蜂电影|蜜蜂电影]]》作宣传]]

《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的杰夫·拉布雷克（{{lang|en|Jeff Labrecque}}）认为《杰飞的视野》以一种巧妙而又讽刺的方式把宋飞融入其中<ref name="ewreview">{{cite web |url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2007/10/05/mini-tv-watch-3/ |title=''30 Rock'': Pull Yourself Together, Man |accessdate=2013-08-22 |last=Labrecque |first=Jeff |date=2007-10-05 |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130616032744/http://popwatch.ew.com/2007/10/05/mini-tv-watch-3/ |archivedate=2013-06-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[电视指南_(美国杂志)|电视指南]]的马特·韦伯·米托维奇（{{lang|en|Matt Webb Mitovich}}）称赞《宋飞的视野》给这季奠定了一个坚实的基础，其中的确拥有不少“非常、非常精彩的瞬间”。不过，韦伯·米托维奇批评了剧中肯尼斯和崔西的“办公室老婆”故事线索，表示这样的题材并不新鲜，之前已经有过许多情景喜剧使用，而且《宋飞的视野》中对这一部分的处理有些过于草率，收到的喜剧效果也很差。他还批评剧中的简娜身穿横条纹的服装却又试图避免让节目的一众编剧发觉自己变胖的情节并不好笑<ref name="tvguidereview">{{cite web |url=http://community.tvguide.com/blog-entry/TV-Show-Blog/30-Rock/Episode-Recap-Seinfeldvision/800023766 |title=Episode Recap: 'SeinfeldVision' |accessdate=2008-03-29 |last=Mitovich |first=Matt Webb |date=2007-10-04 |publisher=''TV Guide'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071112044838/http://community.tvguide.com/blog-entry/TV-Show-Blog/30-Rock/Episode-Recap-Seinfeldvision/800023766 |archivedate=2007-11-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[Television_Without_Pity|Television Without Pity]]}}网站的丽莎·施梅瑟（{{lang|en|Lisa Schmeiser}}）给予这集节目B+的评价<ref name="twopreview">{{cite web |url=http://www.televisionwithoutpity.com/show/30-rock/seinfeldvision/?currentPage=1 |title='SeinfeldVision' |accessdate=2008-03-29 |last=Schmeiser |first=Lisa |date=2007-10-05 |publisher=''Television Without Pity'' |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130822041023/http://www.televisionwithoutpity.com/show/30-rock/seinfeldvision/?currentPage=1 |archive-date=2013-08-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。{{lang|en|Zap2it}}网站的瑞克·波特（{{lang|en|Rick Porter}}）表扬本集给《我为喜剧狂》的第二季划下了浓厚的一笔，他认为这虽然不是该剧至今最优秀的一集，但仍然是电视上表现最抢眼的喜剧作品之一<ref name="zap2itreview">{{cite web |url=http://blog.zap2it.com/ithappenedlastnight/2007/10/30-rock-now-in-.html |title=''30 Rock,'' now in 'SeinfeldVision'! |accessdate=2008-03-29 |last=Porter |first=Rick |date=2007-10-04 |publisher=''Zap2it'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090113181134/http://blog.zap2it.com/ithappenedlastnight/2007/10/30-rock-now-in-.html |archivedate=2009-01-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[美国在线|美国在线]]电视小队的鲍勃·萨松尼（{{lang|en|Bob Sassone}}）称《宋飞的视野》给了第二季一个非常有趣的开始，他还指出杰瑞·宋飞的出场感觉不像是由替身演出的，并称赞剧中有关杰瑞能够以400万[[美元|美元]]的价格买下全国广播公司的笑话正是他“喜欢这个节目的原因之一”<ref name="tvsquadreview">{{cite web |url=http://www.aoltv.com/2007/10/04/30-rock-seinfeldvision-season-premiere/ |title=''30 Rock'': 'SeinfeldVision' (Season Premiere) |accessdate=2013-08-22 |first=Bob |last=Sassone |date=2007-10-04 |publisher=AOL's ''TV Squad'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120820045939/http://www.aoltv.com/2007/10/04/30-rock-seinfeldvision-season-premiere/ |archivedate=2012-08-20 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《[[匹兹堡邮报|匹兹堡邮报]]》的罗布·欧文（{{lang|en|Rob Owen}}）称这集节目证明这部收视率较低剧集所赢得的[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]最佳喜剧可谓实至名归<ref name="ppgreview">{{cite web |url=http://www.post-gazette.com/stories/ae/tv/tv-review-30-rock-rolls-with-smart-commentary-504611/ |title=TV Review: ''30 Rock'' Rolls with Smart Commentary |accessdate=2013-08-22 |last=Owen |first=Rob |date=2007-10-04 |publisher=''Pittsburgh Post-Gazette'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121006153803/http://www.post-gazette.com/stories/ae/tv/tv-review-30-rock-rolls-with-smart-commentary-504611/ |archivedate=2012-10-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《{{link-en|明星纪事报|The Star-Ledger}}》的阿兰·塞平沃尔（{{lang|en|Alan Sepinwall}}）形容本集节目“非常有趣”，每个人都有让人信服的发挥<ref name="slreview">{{cite web |url=http://blog.nj.com/alltv/2007/10/30_rock_baby_got_front.html |title=''30 Rock'': Baby Got Front |accessdate=2013-08-22 |last=Sepinwall |first=Alan |date=2007-10-04 |publisher=''The Star-Ledger'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120210040448/http://blog.nj.com/alltv/2007/10/30_rock_baby_got_front.html |archivedate=2012-02-10 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《[[纽约邮报|纽约邮报]]》的琳达·斯塔西（{{lang|en|Linda Stasi}}）称节目让她笑得甚至多次从床上摔下来<ref name="nypreview">{{cite web |url=http://www.nypost.com/p/entertainment/tv/item_i381JypkE38X0DhhbaWuXN;jsessionid=C68C032715F48D3E57BC4E1697B53206 |title=What a 'Deal'! |accessdate=2013-08-22 |last=Stasi |first=Linda |date=2007-10-04 |publisher=''The New York Post'' }}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。《{{link-en|纽约观察|The New York Observer}}》的杰克·布鲁克斯（{{lang|en|Jake Brooks}}）认为这22[[分钟|分钟]]的节目里除杰瑞·宋飞出场的部分表现不佳外，其它时段都很出色<ref name="nyoreview">{{cite web |url=http://observer.com/2007/10/was-seinfelds-stint-i30-rockis-way-of-jumping-the-shark/ |title=Was Seinfeld's Stint ''30 Rock''s Way of Jumping the Shark? |accessdate=2013-08-22 |last=Brooks |first=Jake |date=2007-10-05 |publisher=''The New York Observer'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130709065952/http://observer.com/2007/10/was-seinfelds-stint-i30-rockis-way-of-jumping-the-shark/ |archivedate=2013-07-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[IGN|IGN]]网站的罗伯特·坎宁（{{lang|en|Robert Canning}}）认为这集节目给新季《我为喜剧狂》一个良好的开始，并希望节目能够吸引到更多的观众来长久地播出下去，他最终给这一集9.4的高分（最高为10）<ref name="ignreview">{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/10/03/30-rock-seinfeldvision-advance-review |title=''30 Rock'': 'SeinfeldVision' Advance Review |accessdate=2013-08-22 |last=Canning |first=Robert |date=2007-10-03 |publisher=''IGN'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120210055557/http://tv.ign.com/articles/824/824655p1.html |archivedate=2012-02-10 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《[[综艺|综艺]]》杂志的布莱恩·洛瑞（{{lang|en|Brian Lowry}}）称赞《宋飞的视野》巧妙地表现出了《我为喜剧狂》的长处和弱点，亚历克·鲍德温的聪明才智提升了节目的档次，并且也减少了很多愚蠢而让人厌烦的内容<ref name="varietyreview">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2007/film/reviews/30-rock-5-1200555695/ |title=''30 Rock'' (Series – NBC, Thurs. Oct. 4, 8:30PM) |accessdate=2013-08-22 |last=Lowry |first=Brian |date=2007-10-03 |publisher=''Variety'' |archive-date=2013-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130822050157/http://variety.com/2007/film/reviews/30-rock-5-1200555695/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《纽约时报》的亚历山大·斯坦利（{{lang|en|Alessandra Stanley}}）认为《宋飞的视野》证明，即便最有才华的演员和编剧在压力之下也会有表现失常的时候<ref name="nytimesreview">{{cite web |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9D01E0DE1F3EF937A35753C1A9619C8B63&partner=rssnyt&emc=rss |title=''30 Rock'' and ''Grey's Anatomy''; Sophomore Jitters and 'SeinfeldVision' |accessdate=2013-08-22 |last=Stanley |first=Alessandra |date=2007-10-04 |publisher=''The New York Times'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024010050/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9D01E0DE1F3EF937A35753C1A9619C8B63&partner=rssnyt&emc=rss |archivedate=2012-10-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，斯坦利批评杰瑞·宋飞利用自己在剧中的出场给电影《蜜蜂电影》作宣传，对此宋飞、全国广播公司和[[通用电气|通用电气]]都表示这只是一个玩笑<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/10/03/us-seinfeld-idUSN0243829420071003 |title=Seinfeld Plugs Own Movie in ''30 Rock'' Guest Spot |accessdate=2013-08-22 |last=Gorman |first=Steve |date=2007-10-03 |publisher=''Reuters'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121112225854/http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/10/03/us-seinfeld-idUSN0243829420071003 |archivedate=2012-11-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

